                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-279-victim2313 t18300916-279-viclabel1421"></join>. I lost my tools on the 4th of August, from <placeName id="t18300916-279-crimeloc1422">Staples' Inn</placeName>
